Troubleshooting

#Note
you have to enter a value in the prompt.for example 
Enter weekly budget:40(you have to enter value 40)

If you encounter any errors during compilation or execution, double-check the following:

Make sure you have correctly installed the Java Development Kit (JDK).
Verify that you are using the correct commands for compilation (javac) and execution (java).
Ensure that your Java program file has the correct filename and is located in the directory you are working in.
